title: TheForum.ws Presents: The Best Rock Collection | 10 CD Set
description:
120 Hand-Picked Songs, VBR, nothing very heavy so it's a good collection for casual listening. Please thank TheForum.ws which has supplied album art to go along with it.





Note: When you import these into itunes, it won't show individual artists, but one big 'compilation'. If you wish to change this; Highlight all the songs (Ctrl + A) > Right click > Get info. Go to the 'options' tab, and change 'part of a compilation' to 'no'.


Another Note: I have went through and made sure all the 'Artist' and 'Title' tags are correct. If you remove it from a compilation, everything will be nicely organized by artist and song name.
